chs Prinzipien des einfachen Bauens.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 27. Okt 2021) 4aBaumaterial. 4aDämmbeton. 4aEnergieeffizienz. 4aKlimaschutz. 4aKonstruktion. 4aLow Tech. 4aMassivholzbau. 4aWohnen. 4aWohnhaus. 4aZiegelbau. 7aARCHITECTURE / Methods & Materials.2bisacsh  aInfra-lightweight concrete, energy efficiency, climate protection, construction, low-tech, timber work, building materials, housing, brick building.1 aNagler, Florian, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt0 cprintz978303562464940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783035624663423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783035624663/original  aEBA_CL_AD  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_AD  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_ESTMALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA18STMEE  aPDA5EBK